# Student Record System using Constructors (C++)

## Overview
This project demonstrates the use of constructors in C++ to manage student records.

## Features
- Add student using parameterized constructor
- Display all student records

## Concepts Used
- Classes and Objects
- Default Constructor
- Parameterized Constructor
- Vectors

## How to Run
1. Compile:
   g++ main.cpp -o main

2. Run:
   ./main